text: Michael Reihs (born 25 April 1979) is a Danish former professional racing cyclist. ==Major results== ;2005 : 2nd CSC Classic : 6th GP Herning ;2006 : 3rd La Roue Tourangelle : 6th GP Herning ;2007 : 2nd Internatie Reninghelst : 3rd Boucle de l'Artois : 7th GP Herning ;2008 : 7th Ronde van Overijssel ;2009 : 2nd Classic Loire Atlantique : 2nd GP Herning : 6th GP Bikebuster : 8th Nokere Koerse : 10th Paris–Troyes ;2010 : 1st Stage 6 La Tropicale Amissa Bongo : 4th Rogaland GP : 5th GP Herning : 7th La Roue Tourangelle : 9th Grand Prix de la Ville de Pérenchies ;2011 : 1st Himmerland Rundt : 2nd GP Herning : 3rd Road race, National Road Championships : 6th Tartu GP ;2012 : 5th Himmerland Rundt ;2013 : 9th GP Herning ;2015 : 6th GP Horsens ;2016 : 8th GP Horsens ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Danish male cyclists Category:People from Silkeborg
title: Michael Reihs
